text: Kirsty Leigh-Brown (born 13 November 1981) is an Australian gymnast. She competed in five events at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:Australian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Australia Category:Gymnasts at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Albury, New South Wales
